readme:
Service Usage

SV577 Retrieve External Logon Details provides departmental systems with the details of an external user (eg. name, email address, assigned roles etc..)

Service Behaviour

The service will retrieve details of an external used based on the supplied identifier information

Service Flow

A normal flow for this service is for Subscription to invokemSV577 for a specific ESS user. If the supplied user identifier matches a valid user, ESS will response with the details of the user, if not an error message will be sent.

Transformation

N/A
